    {
      "id": 1,
      "translated": "\"Yes.\""
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "translated": "\"I'm so unused to seeing myself like this, I can't tell if it actually suits me.\""
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "translated": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "translated": "\"But... I've always wanted to wear something like this.\""
    },
    {
