      "translated": "\"But ever since I was little, I never owned anything cute.\""
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "translated": "\"I didn't think they'd suit me, and I had this bias that I was more of a 'cool' type, so I could never bring myself to say I liked cute things.\""
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "translated": "\"There was one time I worked up the courage to wear one.\""
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "translated": "\"A cute dress just like this.\""
