      "translated": "This one is from Meshi-san."
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "translated": "Thank you so much."
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "translated": "\"Hello, Sato-san! Kon-Niigo!\""
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "translated": "\"I'm always having a great time playing ProSeka.\""
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "translated": "\"The 4-star illustrations this time, especially Mizuki's, were so good that I went all out on the gacha to get them.\""
