    {
      "id": 13,
      "translated": "Here, here... oh, here!"
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "translated": "This thing right here is called a torso."
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "translated": "It's the torso from 'Reaching Out for an Unbreakable Tomorrow'."
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "translated": "\"Anyway, Mizuki was in a space with torsos again.\""
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "translated": "\"Usually, the torso space represents Mizuki's dark feelings,\""
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "translated": "\"but this time, it felt like a space representing Mizuki's bright, cheerful heart,\""
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "translated": "\"looking forward after feeling the warmth of family, Niigo, and friends.\""
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "translated": "\"I was so happy to see this change in Mizuki's state of mind.\""
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "translated": "\"I can't thank the staff enough for creating such wonderful illustrations and scenarios, nor the voice actors for their deep, empathetic performances.\""
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "translated": "\"Thank you for always creating such wonderful events.\""
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "translated": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "translated": "\"Please take care of yourselves and keep up the good work.\""
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "translated": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "translated": "\"I'll keep supporting Niigo!\" That's what they wrote."
