    {
      "id": 29,
      "translated": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "translated": "The colors in these illustrations are quite rare for Niigo, aren't they?"
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "translated": "We've had pale colors before, but..."
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "translated": "Seeing Niigo bathed in sunlight is special."
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "translated": "I mean, they don't really go outside much to begin with,"
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
      "translated": "so seeing Niigo during the day felt very fresh to me."
    },
    {
      "id": 35,
      "translated": "Usually, you don't see them like this."
    },
    {
      "id": 36,
      "translated": "I thought it was a really nice touch."
    },
    {
      "id": 37,
      "translated": "And it wasn't just Mizuki; everyone looked great."
    },
    {
      "id": 38,
      "translated": "Both the pre-trained and trained versions made me realize what amazing artists we have."
    },
    {
      "id": 39,
      "translated": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 40,
      "translated": "I'm truly grateful for them."
    },
    {
      "id": 41,
      "translated": "And this time,"
    },
    {
      "id": 42,
      "translated": "we've received comments from the illustration team regarding the outfits,"
