    {
      "id": 47,
      "translated": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 48,
      "translated": "\"Mizuki, having been accepted by Niigo, wants to create clothes that can help children who have similar worries,\""
    },
    {
      "id": 49,
      "translated": "\"or children who can't bring themselves to like who they are.\""
    },
    {
      "id": 50,
      "translated": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 51,
      "translated": "\"Inspired by the story of Mizuki thinking about a future career in fashion, we wanted to express the image of a future they've started to envision.\""
