    {
      "id": 53,
      "translated": "\"We chose a simple yet elegant one-piece dress design.\""
    },
    {
      "id": 54,
      "translated": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 55,
      "translated": "\"As a special touch, we added the yellow daisy embroidery used in Mizuki's initial unit outfit.\""
    },
    {
      "id": 56,
      "translated": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 57,
      "translated": "\"By including this, we wanted to convey a message of being true to oneself.\""
    },
    {
      "id": 58,
      "translated": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 59,
      "translated": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 60,
      "translated": "\"This resulted in a simple design that is uniquely Mizuki's.\""
    },
    {
      "id": 61,
      "translated": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 62,
      "translated": "\"Furthermore, to reflect the song's calm, warm impression and Mizuki's budding hope for the future,\""
