    {
      "id": 63,
      "translated": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 64,
      "translated": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 65,
      "translated": "\"we used a palette of pale, gentle colors.\""
    },
    {
      "id": 66,
      "translated": "That's what the team said."
    },
    {
      "id": 67,
      "translated": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 68,
      "translated": "It's true, the overall color scheme for everyone is quite pale this time."
    },
    {
      "id": 69,
      "translated": "I see!"
    },
    {
      "id": 70,
      "translated": "Did you all notice that the daisy was included?"
    },
    {
      "id": 71,
      "translated": "Did you catch that?"
    },
    {
